  <chunk id="1968f8d8ffe3f695372d919c9966b1ca412b83d2.c2" text="Our results indicate that upregulation of COX-2 by HBV and HBx is mediated by both demethylation events and recruitment of multiple transcription factors binding to the promoter."/>
